<paragraph blockId="15.[188,1400,1608,1776]" pageId="15" pageNumber="60">
FEMALE GENITALIA. Tergite IX (
<figureCitation box="[554,714,1608,1635]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="15.[189,232,1416,1442]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,266,1389]" captionTargetId="figure-189@15.[189,1398,265,1391]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="Fig. 8. Andes latanalus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♀. A. Genitalia, lateral view. B. Genitalia, ventral view. C. Anal segment, dorsal view. D. Tergite IX, caudal view. E. Gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, dorsal view. F. Gonapophysis IX, lateral view. G. Gonoplac, inner lateral view. H. Posterior vagina, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862191" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862191/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="60">Fig. 8A–B, D</figureCitation>
) moderately sclerotized, with a large, nearly elliptical wax plate. Anal segment (
<figureCitation box="[442,533,1644,1670]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="15.[189,232,1416,1442]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,266,1389]" captionTargetId="figure-189@15.[189,1398,265,1391]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="Fig. 8. Andes latanalus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♀. A. Genitalia, lateral view. B. Genitalia, ventral view. C. Anal segment, dorsal view. D. Tergite IX, caudal view. E. Gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, dorsal view. F. Gonapophysis IX, lateral view. G. Gonoplac, inner lateral view. H. Posterior vagina, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862191" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862191/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="60">Fig. 8C</figureCitation>
) rectangular, 1.6 × as long as wide in dorsal view, anal style linguiform. Gonapophysis IX (
<figureCitation box="[420,509,1679,1705]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="15.[189,232,1416,1442]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,266,1389]" captionTargetId="figure-189@15.[189,1398,265,1391]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="Fig. 8. Andes latanalus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♀. A. Genitalia, lateral view. B. Genitalia, ventral view. C. Anal segment, dorsal view. D. Tergite IX, caudal view. E. Gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, dorsal view. F. Gonapophysis IX, lateral view. G. Gonoplac, inner lateral view. H. Posterior vagina, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862191" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862191/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="60">Fig. 8F</figureCitation>
) with one middle tooth, distance ratio between middle tooth to apex and length of denticulate portion 2.0. Gonoplac (
<figureCitation box="[729,823,1714,1740]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="15.[189,232,1416,1442]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,266,1389]" captionTargetId="figure-189@15.[189,1398,265,1391]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="Fig. 8. Andes latanalus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♀. A. Genitalia, lateral view. B. Genitalia, ventral view. C. Anal segment, dorsal view. D. Tergite IX, caudal view. E. Gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, dorsal view. F. Gonapophysis IX, lateral view. G. Gonoplac, inner lateral view. H. Posterior vagina, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862191" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862191/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="60">Fig. 8G</figureCitation>
) rod-like, 4.4× as long as wide in lateral view. Posterior vagina pattern as shown in 
<figureCitation box="[622,715,1749,1775]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="15.[189,232,1416,1442]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,266,1389]" captionTargetId="figure-189@15.[189,1398,265,1391]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="Fig. 8. Andes latanalus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♀. A. Genitalia, lateral view. B. Genitalia, ventral view. C. Anal segment, dorsal view. D. Tergite IX, caudal view. E. Gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, dorsal view. F. Gonapophysis IX, lateral view. G. Gonoplac, inner lateral view. H. Posterior vagina, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862191" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862191/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="60">Fig. 8H</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
